'There is no third party involved, and Ben and Abby now ask that their privacy and that of their family be respected at this difficult time.'

The couple, who wed in 2003 after eight years together, have two daughters together.

While it isn't clear how long ago they parted ways, Ben has been spotted at several events in London over the past week, including the Julien Macdonald London Fashion Week show last Friday and the Dot Com Children's Fund Charity Gala on Tuesday.

