News of Ben's split will no doubt fuel what some have dubbed 'the curse of Strictly' after many celebrity contestants' marriages and relationships have broken down following the show.

Ben's fellow 2013 contestant Susanna Reid's long-term relationship with the father of her children ended following her appearance on Strictly.

In November last year, Countdown presenter Rachel Riley revealed her marriage had ended and earlier this month went public with her Strictly professional partner Pasha Kovalev as a couple.

The new series of Strictly hasn't even begun and two celebrity contestants Simon Webbe and Sunetra Sarker have also announced their love splits.

